Html:
It appears that the AccountController.cs used in the Assets folder for 3.0b doesn't match the same thing in the code directory.  Looks like the Assets didn't include the checked in code from 4/18.  A minor nit is also the difference in sort order of SampleData.cs.

Different files:

Controllers\AccountController.cs - release includes call to MigrateShoppingCart, assets does not

Models\SampleData.cs - release has different order of album data ("The Best of Men At Work" is first)
